name: SNPs
tagline: Public Resrouces Related to Clinical Impacts of SNPs
body:
### Functional Impact Predictors 
[Consensus Path DB](http://consensuspathdb.org/)  
[Evolutionary Couplings](http://evfold.org/evfold-web/evfold.do)  

### Structural Variants 
[BMC Bioinformatics](http://bmcbioinformatics.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/1471-2105-12-151)  

### Metadata 
[Observational Health Data Sciences and Informatics](http://www.ohdsi.org/data-standardization/the-common-data-model/)  

### Other SNP Annotators and Callers 
[SNP In](http://andromeda.rnet.missouri.edu/snpintool/index.php/welcome)  
[Digenic Disease Database](http://dida.ibsquare.be)  
[VariBench](http://structure.bmc.lu.se/VariBench/)   
[Variation Ontology](https://bioportal.bioontology.org/ontologies/VARIO)  
[VariSNP](http://structure.bmc.lu.se/VariSNP/)  
[PON-Sol](https://omictools.com/pon-sol-tool)  

### Network Analyses et al
[Combined Annotation Dependednt Depletion](http://cadd.gs.washington.edu/)  
Adaboost  
[ToppGene](https://toppgene.cchmc.org/)   
[motifbreakR](https://www.bioconductor.org/packages/devel/bioc/html/motifbreakR.html)   
[remuRNA](http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/CBBresearch/Przytycka/index.cgi#remurna)   
[Simmons Center for Quantitative Biology](http://qb.cshl.edu)   

### Structure Stuff
[ConTemplate](http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/26455800)  
[Pro-Maya](http://omictools.com/protein-mutant-stability-analyzer-tool)  
[Deogon](http://ibsquare.be/deogen)   

### RNAseq Stuff
[BrainSpan](http://www.brainspan.org/rnaseq/search/index.html)   
[Geo2Enrichr](http://amp.pharm.mssm.edu/g2e/)   
[Enrichr](http://amp.pharm.mssm.edu/Enrichr/)   

### Cancer Genomics 
[MutSigCV](http://www.broadinstitute.org/cancer/software/genepattern/modules/docs/MutSigCV)   
[CHASM2](http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2763410/)   

### Pharmacogenomics 
EMPIRIC -- effects on drug binding
